Audit Team Leader - PT Pacific Fiber Indonesia
Audit Team Leader  -
Audit Team Leader
Responsibilities
Conduct internal audit reviews of the companies within the Group.Key duties include process documentation, risk identification & assessment as well as evaluation of the adequacy and effectiveness of internal controls.Check for compliance with established Group policies and procedures.Prepare Audit Reports.Follow up on implementation of management action plans.Participate in other projects which may include fraud investigation.Lead project team consisting of 2 - 3 Internal Auditors, as assigned by and under supervision of Lead Auditor and Audit Manager.  Degree in Accountancy, Finance, or equivalent.At least 4 years of audit experience in a large organization or an international public accounting firm, with 2 years experience in managing team or subordinates.Good command of written and spoken English.Willing to be placed in Kalimantan/ Pekanbaru/ Balikpapan/ Medan.
